Cook peas until crisp-tender as directed on package. Drain; rinse with cold water to cool. In large bowl, combine peas and all remaining salad ingredients; mix well. In small bowl, combine all dressing ingredients; mix well. Add to salad; toss to mix. Refrigerate 1 hour or until chilled. Line individual salad plates or serving bowls with kale. Spoon salad onto kale. Garnish with green onion and bell pepper.